---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — Zurhaar Tools" description="Terms of service for Zurhaar Tools products and services.">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-10">Last updated: April 27, 2026</p>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Overview</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            These terms govern your use of products and services sold through zurhaartools.com, operated by Zurhaar Tools (eenmanszaak), KVK 42045392, based in the Netherlands. By making a purchase, you agree to these terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Products and delivery</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Zurhaar Tools sells digital products including browser extensions, scripts, templates, and tools. Products are delivered instantly after payment:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-muted">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent shrink-0"></span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Credit-based products</strong> — you receive a license key by email and on the confirmation page immediately after checkout. Credits are added to your account and never expire.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent shrink-0"></span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Downloadable products</strong> — you receive a download link by email immediately after checkout.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Payments</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Payments are processed securely by <a href="https://stripe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">Stripe</a>. We do not store or have access to your payment card details. All prices are listed in euros (EUR). Applicable taxes may be added at checkout depending on your location.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Right of withdrawal and refunds</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Under EU consumer law, you have a 14-day right of withdrawal for online purchases. However, by completing your purchase you acknowledge and consent that:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-muted mb-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent shrink-0"></span>
              <span>Digital content is delivered immediately after payment</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent shrink-0"></span>
              <span>You waive your 14-day right of withdrawal once delivery begins</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            If you experience technical issues that prevent you from using a product, contact us at <a href="mailto:andreas@zurhaartools.com" class="text-primary-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">andreas@zurhaartools.com</a> and we will resolve the issue or provide a refund.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">5. License and usage</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Each purchase grants you a personal, non-transferable license to use the product. You may not redistribute, resell, or share your license key with others. One license key is intended for one user.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Product availability</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We strive to keep all products available and functional. However, we reserve the right to discontinue or modify products. If a product you purchased is discontinued, your existing credits or licenses will remain valid.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Our products are provided "as is." While we aim for accuracy, we do not guarantee that analysis results (such as job posting scans) are complete or error-free. Our tools are intended as an aid, not as professional advice. Zurhaar Tools is not liable for decisions made based on product output.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">8. Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Your privacy is important to us. Please refer to our <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a> for details on how we handle your data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">9. Governing law</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            These terms are governed by Dutch law. Any disputes will be resolved through the competent court in the Netherlands.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">10. Changes to these terms</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            We may update these terms from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. Continued use of our products after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
            Zurhaar Tools<br>
            KVK: 42045392<br>
            Email: <a href="mailto:andreas@zurhaartools.com" class="text-primary-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">andreas@zurhaartools.com</a><br>
            Web: <a href="https://zurhaartools.com" class="text-primary-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">zurhaartools.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
